    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hmm, I think the previous behaviour actually wasn't the correct one, since it's supposed to limit the last page to go to, so it's surprising that this gives you the experience you wanted. \r\n\r\nI can definitely see the use case for showing only the pagers though. One option is to use the connector to make your own, the second option is that we should consider an option to have the behaviour you want; maybe padding: -1 ? ",
