    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I was kind of expecting to hear that the original behavior was the real bug. A more direct boolean option sounds great. Using negative value on the padding option would be fine but less clear and obvious. \r\n\r\nIn the meantime we’ll see if we can make a custom version using the connector. Thanks!",
